description: Saying goodbye is extremely hard for us who truly loved Kobe.The unexpected loss of Kobe left us immense pain and sorrow. What would you do to commemorate this great player. Yes, we are going to revive him! All the people who loved Kobe, all the people who were inspired by Mamba Mentality, please join us. We need your help!
